      "width": 620,
      "height": 280,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Skill: BatchMutation\n\n**Authority:** Normative\n\nApply many mutations as a single logical, reversible operation.\n\nThis skill defines how atomic change is allowed to occur.\n\nThis graph is the contract.",
